{"tid":1825392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《成績表》去年逾5590萬人次訪港　按年跌14.2%","createTime":"2020-01-15T08:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T10:34:20.000Z","uid":180114,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0281e51d216358d5907f311177204f32dc53171d","tid":1825392,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】旅發局公佈去年訪港旅客數字，逾5590萬人次，按年下跌14.2%。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局數字顯示，2019年上半年訪港旅客，錄得13.9%的增長，但受社會事件影響，旅客數字自7月起下跌。<br />\n<br />\n隨後的月份跌勢加劇，下半年整體訪港旅客下跌39.1%，其中內地及短途市場跌幅最明顯，分別下跌14.2%及18.7%。整體訪港過夜旅客亦跌近兩成，達2376萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=376864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376864&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=20e835ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376864&h=fc4434a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=376864</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 